Quickstrike:





"Tran--" Quickstrike cut himself short, hearing Megatron voice. He turned 
his head to see not Megatron, but a scrawny drone. "Boss? That you?" If he 
had the stength and guts, he would laugh. He listened, reluctantly as he 
asked him for the codes for Hell Beast's ship. "The codes? Boss, ah ain't 
gonna give you th' codes. Ah ain't riskin' it. What ya want wit' 'em?"
